sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Producer Service
    participant B as Celery Broker (Redis)
    participant W as Worker Process

    Note over P: set_trace_context(trace_id, span_id)

    P->>P: task.delay() / apply_async()
    P->>P: before_task_publish signal fires
    P->>P: inject_trace_headers() → adds trace_id,<br/>parent_span_id, traceparent to message headers

    P->>B: Publish task message (with trace headers)

    B->>W: Deliver message

    W->>W: task_prerun signal fires
    W->>W: extract_trace_from_task_headers(request.headers)
    W->>W: set_trace_context(trace_id, parent_span_id,<br/>task_id, task_name)
    W->>W: Log "Task started" with trace_id

    Note over W: Task body executes<br/>(TraceContextFilter injects trace_id<br/>into all log records)

    alt Success
        W->>W: task_postrun signal fires
        W->>W: Log "Task completed" with latency_ms
        W->>W: clear_trace_context()
    else Failure
        W->>W: task_failure signal fires
        W->>W: Log "Task failed" with error info
        Note over W: ⚠️ clear_trace_context() NOT called (bug)
    else Retry
        W->>W: task_retry signal fires
        W->>W: Log "Task retrying" with retry_reason
    end
